OL,3,CUnited fan admits slapping City's
OL,4,CGrealish
OL,6,FA football fan has admitted assaulting
OL,7,FManchester City and England star Jack
OL,8,FGrealish by slapping his face.
OL,10,FAlfie Holt, 20, pleaded guilty to a
OL,11,Fsingle count of assault on Grealish,
OL,12,Fwho he said had insulted him, calling
OL,13,Fhim a "little ugly w****r", after the
OL,14,FManchester Derby in April, Manchester
OL,15,FMagistrates' Court heard.
OL,17,FThe defendant, a Manchester United
OL,18,Ffan, of Droylsden, Tameside, told the
OL,19,Fcourt: "I did not expect him to say
OL,20,Fwhat he said to me and I have reacted.
OL,21,FI regret it. That's it."
