OL,6,FShazia Aslam, prosecuting, told the
OL,7,Fcourt Grealish was leaving the field
OL,8,Fafter the Manchester Derby at Old
OL,9,FTrafford, which had a sell-out crowd
OL,10,Fand was always a "contentious affair."
OL,12,FShe added: "Both sets of fans were
OL,13,Fvery vocal, shouting abusive comments
OL,14,Fto rival players."
OL,16,FThe court heard that as players left
OL,17,Fthe field, heading for the tunnel,
OL,18,FHolt stood very close by, shouting
OL,19,Fabuse at Manchester City players.
