OL,6,F"As the complainant, Jack Grealish, a
OL,7,FMan City player, enters the tunnel
OL,8,Farea, he hears the defendant shouting
OL,9,Fcomments towards him. He turns and
OL,10,Fwalks towards him. Both have an
OL,11,Fexchange of words.
OL,13,F"As the complainant walks away, the
OL,14,Fdefendant slaps the complainant across
OL,15,Fthe face. There was no injury. He was
OL,16,Farrested outside the stadium."
