OL,6,FHe told police he was shouting abuse
OL,7,Fat Manchester City players, including
OL,8,FPhil Foden, who ignored him.
OL,10,FHe then shouted, "k***head" at
OL,11,FGrealish, who reacted and a "verbal
OL,12,Faltercation took place," the court
OL,13,Fheard.
OL,15,FHolt told police Grealish said to him:
OL,16,F"You little, ugly w****r," and he
OL,17,F"flipped" and reached out and slapped
OL,18,Fthe footballer.
OL,20,FMagistrates were shown a brief clip of
OL,21,Fthe incident, which had no sound.
