OL,6,FMs Aslam added: "The defendant uses
OL,7,Fforce against a player. Players are
OL,8,Fextremely vulnerable to this sort of
OL,9,Fconduct and need to be protected."
OL,11,FHolt, a Manchester United season
OL,12,Fticket holder in the Stretford End,
OL,13,Fwas also given a three-year Football
OL,14,FBanning Order and was fined #120, with
OL,15,F#85 costs and a surcharge of #48.
OL,17,FMelanie Winstantley, defending, said
OL,18,FHolt had no previous convictions and
OL,19,Fhad never been arrested before, so the
OL,20,Fincident was completely out of
OL,21,Fcharacter for him.
